summary: There’s no other singer even half as special as Taylor
body:
There’s no other singer even half as special as Taylor

Like name a singer that’s made you feel better or that does more for us, she works for us everyday and then she gets online and likes our photos and checks on us to see what we’re doing. She makes us all feel important and that’s the best part. Name a better tour. Name a singer with more individualism

Just try to compare the other singers to Taylor, because it’s hard

@taylorswift @taylornation
